


                       YAM - Croatian charset translation
                Addition to WarpHRII - Croatian font localization



--------- ---------
HRVATSKI: CROATIAN:
--------- ---------

 Koristite ove prijevode obavezno, jer s time dobijate pravilan HEADER u YAM-u,
tako da vaši prijatelji s drugih platformi mogu èitati vašu poštu kako je vi
vidite.


 Uputa:

 · U CROSCII æete rijetko trebati, npr. ako redovito šaljete poruke na BBS-ove
    preko interneta, i to ako primalac koristi CROSCII fontove
 · U ASCII æete vjerojatno rijetko trebati, iz sliènog razloga. Ako se dvoumite
    izmeðu ASCII i CROSCII, izaberite ASCII, neæete pogriješiti
 · Fontove za ove charsete naravno možete naæi na WWWWarpu;
    http://islands.zesoi.fer.hr/~dpuljiz/warp, a tamo kliknite na [Kanta]
 · Latin2 su fontovi s ekstenzijom '-LII' iz iste arhive, Win1250 su fontovi bez
    ekstenzije, i oni se koriste po defaultu
 · Preporuka: stavite Latin2 -> Win1250, ili Latin2 -> Win1250 što znaèi da i vi
    možete èitati, i vaši frendovi na drugim platformama (najvjerojatnije)


--------- ---------
ENGLISH:  ENGLESKI:
--------- ---------

 You should use this charsets translationa, since you get regular HEADER in YAM
outgoing mail, and this way you make sure your ‘other-platform’ friends may read
your mail as you see it.


 Usage:

 · To CROSCII option; rarely used, i.e. in case you send your messges to BBS'
    overt the internet on regular (daily) basis, in addition to that,
    recipient has to use CROSCII fonts
 · To ASCII option; same as above, but if you're in doubt which one to use, I
    suggest you go for ASCII, this way you cannot go wrong about it
 · All the fonts you need you got on WWWWarp site;
               http://islands.zesoi.fer.hr/~dpuljiz/warp,
    click at [Kanta], and follow the links outthere
 · Latin2 are the fonts w/ extension '-LII' from archive above, Win1250 are
    normal fonts, and they are used by default
 · Advised: use Latin2 -> Win1250, or Latin2 -> Win1250



